				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}${\gamma ^{xy}} = \sqrt {- g} {g^{xy}}$\end{document} as a linearized wave propagates cleanly through the spherical injection boundary and passes to the characteristic grid, where it is propagated to \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
